      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mastercard-reaches-agreement-principle-settle-mass-uk-fees-case-2024-12-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[万事达卡周二表示，已就代表英国消费者就卡费问题在伦敦提起的集体诉讼达成原则协议。]]></description>
